WEBVTT

01:40.000 --> 01:43.680
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

01:43.760 --> 01:50.240
REFORM FOR GROWTH

02:00.560 --> 02:03.880
DRIVE SLOWLY, SAFETY FIRST

02:17.400 --> 02:20.000
Sir. Busy? Have a drink.

02:20.080 --> 02:21.040
No, thanks.

02:23.640 --> 02:24.880
Anyway,

02:24.960 --> 02:27.160
did the owner of the factory come today?

02:27.240 --> 02:28.560
Which owner?

02:28.640 --> 02:30.400
Mr. Song Qingsong.

02:31.000 --> 02:33.680
I don't know about that,
but you can't park your car there.

02:33.760 --> 02:35.280
If you're not here to get it fixed,
move it away.

02:35.360 --> 02:36.280
Understood?

02:36.920 --> 02:37.960
Get it fixed.

02:38.040 --> 02:39.040
I'm here to get it fixed.

02:39.120 --> 02:41.680
Look how damaged it is.
Check it and quote a price.

02:44.360 --> 02:45.440
You parked at a great spot.

02:49.040 --> 02:51.240
Your car is seriously damaged.

02:51.760 --> 02:53.080
Did the other person run away?

02:56.440 --> 02:57.800
Stop staring.

02:57.880 --> 02:59.280
You won't see Song here.

02:59.960 --> 03:00.800
Why is that?

03:00.880 --> 03:03.760
Those who can see Song
won't come to me and ask about him.

03:06.440 --> 03:07.800
But isn't it weird?

03:08.560 --> 03:10.640
The place is locked up tight.

03:10.720 --> 03:13.160
And the guard is strong.

03:13.240 --> 03:15.400
One might even say
he's guarding an armory.

03:15.480 --> 03:16.480
Have you not heard?

03:17.000 --> 03:18.360
There was a gang fight here two days ago.

03:18.440 --> 03:19.800
More than 200 men.

03:19.880 --> 03:21.400
It was huge.

03:21.480 --> 03:23.040
I lost some of my wrenches.

03:23.120 --> 03:25.400
A gang fight? With whom?

03:25.480 --> 03:26.640
Cripple Du.

03:27.160 --> 03:28.680
Song's rival.

03:28.760 --> 03:29.800
But why?

03:29.880 --> 03:32.560
For business. The business in the mine.

03:33.680 --> 03:34.720
The mine?

03:35.600 --> 03:36.800
Dongshan Mine?

03:37.720 --> 03:38.920
Do you see another mine in Weiyang?

03:41.960 --> 03:44.200
It's run by the government.
Very lucrative.

03:56.400 --> 03:58.520
QINGSONG CEMENT

04:16.600 --> 04:19.800
PATTIA FRONT DESK

04:19.880 --> 04:21.279
Uncle Ran,

04:21.360 --> 04:22.640
now that we have checked
the underground labyrinth,

04:22.720 --> 04:25.080
it's time to check the labyrinth upstairs.

04:25.880 --> 04:27.920
We need to change our method for that.

04:28.000 --> 04:28.960
Change our method?

04:29.560 --> 04:30.960
We'll use Tremeaux's algorithm.

04:31.040 --> 04:33.240
Tremor? Like land tremors?

04:33.960 --> 04:35.040
Here.

04:35.760 --> 04:39.000
Trémaux's algorithm
is the most time-intensive

04:39.080 --> 04:42.400
yet the most likely to succeed
among all labyrinth solvers.

04:42.480 --> 04:45.680
In short, take every route

04:45.760 --> 04:48.320
and mark them so that we don't make
the same mistake.

04:48.400 --> 04:51.000
In the end, we'll find the exit.

04:51.080 --> 04:53.880
To translate it
into our investigation, it means

04:53.960 --> 04:54.920
we have to first find a lead.

04:55.520 --> 04:58.320
Uncle Ran, you make it sound
too complicated.

04:58.400 --> 05:00.400
Forget about tremors. Just do this.

05:01.560 --> 05:03.760
This is the entrance. This is the exit.

05:04.360 --> 05:06.160
Now, you'll find the solution.

05:09.680 --> 05:10.680
Give it back.

05:25.360 --> 05:27.320
WEIYANG CITY DONGSHAN
MINE OPERATION CONTRACTOR TENDER DOCUMENT

05:27.400 --> 05:28.440
Come in.

05:35.480 --> 05:36.600
Mr. Song.

05:36.680 --> 05:37.640
Hear me out.

05:37.720 --> 05:38.760
Yesterday, I…

05:40.200 --> 05:42.160
You did well last night.

05:43.120 --> 05:44.520
You're smart.

05:47.040 --> 05:48.040
This is your reward.

05:49.200 --> 05:51.160
Mr. Song, I was just doing my job.

05:51.240 --> 05:52.360
So, take it.

05:52.440 --> 05:53.480
I…

05:54.160 --> 05:55.280
Thank you.

06:00.840 --> 06:02.480
When will you return the things
worth hundreds of thousands of yuan

06:02.560 --> 06:03.960
stolen from Yuanlongli?

06:04.560 --> 06:05.560
Immediately.

06:06.080 --> 06:07.280
Immediately.

06:07.880 --> 06:09.880
Where did you bury the woman?

06:11.040 --> 06:13.240
After I was released yesterday,
the police have been following me.

06:13.320 --> 06:14.840
I'll dig out the body now.

06:15.520 --> 06:16.960
Did I tell you to do that?

06:18.080 --> 06:19.400
Are you dumb?

06:19.480 --> 06:21.200
Then, I won't dig the body out. I…

06:21.280 --> 06:22.720
Burn it. Destroy it.

06:22.800 --> 06:25.160
Dissolve it. Deal with it.

06:25.240 --> 06:26.280
Okay.

06:32.280 --> 06:34.680
Take a picture before you get rid of it.

06:34.760 --> 06:35.800
Okay.

06:46.240 --> 06:47.440
AUTO MAINTENANCE, REPAIR SHOP

06:47.520 --> 06:48.680
Mr. Song.

06:48.760 --> 06:50.320
The officer from yesterday
is still waiting outside.

06:50.400 --> 06:51.960
What if he follows me?

06:52.040 --> 06:55.320
You made a mess and you expect me
to clean up after you?

07:02.480 --> 07:05.200
If you fail to handle this properly
and the police find out,

07:05.280 --> 07:06.520
you'll turn yourself in.

07:07.960 --> 07:09.040
Otherwise,

07:10.560 --> 07:12.200
I'll make your family disappear.

07:20.960 --> 07:22.880
Let's see how long you can stay in there.

07:28.480 --> 07:30.600
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

07:36.000 --> 07:38.960
I'M BRINGING XIAOHE TO YUANLONGLI. RAN

07:39.040 --> 07:40.360
Yuanlongli?

07:41.880 --> 07:43.560
Why that place of all places?

07:43.640 --> 07:46.240
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

07:57.120 --> 07:58.200
Stop!

08:01.720 --> 08:02.560
XINFENG AUTO REPAIR

08:11.800 --> 08:13.960
Who told you to do this? You jerk!

08:14.560 --> 08:15.440
Asshole!

08:17.280 --> 08:18.800
Hey! Hey!

08:19.400 --> 08:21.440
Song Qingsong, you son of…

08:29.680 --> 08:30.920
Careful, Xiaohe.

08:37.200 --> 08:38.440
Xiaohe.

08:38.520 --> 08:39.440
Slow down.

08:40.919 --> 08:43.080
Red, orange, yellow, green,

08:43.159 --> 08:44.280
green, blue, purple.

08:44.880 --> 08:46.680
Everyone is here.

09:13.080 --> 09:14.880
Big butt!

09:17.000 --> 09:18.760
-Big butt!
-What are you doing?

09:23.200 --> 09:24.240
Let go!

09:24.320 --> 09:25.600
Let go!

09:31.480 --> 09:33.160
Rat! Pickpocket! Money-grubber!

09:33.240 --> 09:36.480
How come everywhere we go,
we always see you?

09:36.560 --> 09:38.160
It's you again?

09:38.760 --> 09:40.920
Mr. Qian. She is asking your question.

09:41.000 --> 09:42.440
Officer Ran,

09:43.040 --> 09:46.920
someone complained about a stench.

09:47.000 --> 09:48.320
So, I came up here to check.

09:48.400 --> 09:52.600
I thought someone
must have planted something.

09:52.680 --> 09:55.080
Who knew that someone
was raising chickens here?

09:55.160 --> 09:56.200
Unbelievable.

09:58.080 --> 09:59.760
Why did you enter the chicken coop then?

10:00.880 --> 10:02.520
To count the chickens.

10:02.600 --> 10:04.800
How can I fine them without knowing
how many chickens are here?

10:05.400 --> 10:07.480
I'll get someone from the management here.

10:07.560 --> 10:08.800
This is unbelievable.

10:09.400 --> 10:11.080
Unbelievable! I must clean it!

10:13.400 --> 10:15.480
The chicken coop needs to be removed.

10:15.560 --> 10:16.520
Qian!

10:16.600 --> 10:19.440
-How dare you!
-Sir.

10:20.160 --> 10:21.000
Sir.

10:22.680 --> 10:23.600
What are you doing?

10:25.800 --> 10:26.760
Qian Dajun.

10:26.840 --> 10:27.680
Calm down.

10:27.760 --> 10:29.280
Let me make myself clear today.

10:29.360 --> 10:32.160
Touch my chickens
and I'll chop off your hands.

10:32.840 --> 10:34.120
Sir. Calm down.

10:34.200 --> 10:35.520
There's an officer here.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.920
-Calm down.
-I don't care!

10:37.000 --> 10:38.600
-Calm down. Calm down.
-Stay right there.

10:38.680 --> 10:40.560
-Stay right there.
-Calm down.

10:43.240 --> 10:44.320
Calm down.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.600
-That jerk.
-Calm down.

10:48.960 --> 10:51.400
Mister, you're amazing.

10:51.480 --> 10:54.240
Did you raise all these colorful chickens?

10:57.040 --> 11:00.120
Yes. Little girl, do you like them?

11:00.640 --> 11:03.000
If you like them, I can give you one.

11:03.080 --> 11:04.600
Thanks, mister.

11:08.800 --> 11:12.200
Forget about it.
My mother won't let me raise it.

11:13.240 --> 11:14.280
Give me a moment.

11:35.680 --> 11:37.040
Thank you, mister.

11:38.320 --> 11:41.320
I wonder what color this chick will be.

11:41.400 --> 11:42.320
Hey!

11:43.080 --> 11:44.400
It's a raw egg!

12:06.840 --> 12:11.080
DANFENG MIDDLE SCHOOL

12:11.160 --> 12:13.120
PRINCIPAL'S ROOM

12:17.600 --> 12:19.120
Officer He, this is the place.

12:19.200 --> 12:20.080
Thank you.

12:20.160 --> 12:21.160
You're welcome.

12:22.440 --> 12:23.480
Come in.

12:24.480 --> 12:26.960
Hello, Principal Qin. I am He Xiaohe.

12:27.040 --> 12:28.880
I'm here for Han Zi'ang.

12:28.960 --> 12:29.840
Oh.

12:30.360 --> 12:32.480
Officer He. Take a seat.

12:32.560 --> 12:33.680
Thank you.

12:36.400 --> 12:40.240
Principal Qin, I know you're a busy man,
so I'll keep it brief.

12:40.320 --> 12:44.560
I came to urge you
to reconsider the decision

12:44.640 --> 12:46.720
to expel Han Zi'ang.

12:47.600 --> 12:48.760
Officer He.

12:48.840 --> 12:51.240
I already explained to you clearly

12:51.320 --> 12:53.440
in our phone call yesterday.

12:54.400 --> 12:59.080
It's a decision that we made
upon deliberate consideration.

12:59.160 --> 13:00.280
But…

13:01.000 --> 13:02.840
Please let me finish.

13:03.720 --> 13:05.720
The expulsion isn't my decision.

13:06.400 --> 13:09.920
In class, Han Zi'ang dozes off often.

13:10.000 --> 13:12.480
And he often misses classes
for no reason at all.

13:12.560 --> 13:15.200
This time, instead of truancy,

13:15.800 --> 13:18.240
he stabbed someone outside.

13:18.320 --> 13:21.680
Principal Qin, does Han Zi'ang
have a history of violence?

13:23.360 --> 13:24.360
Not that I know of.

13:25.040 --> 13:29.360
His homeroom teacher told us
that he was usually quiet.

13:29.880 --> 13:34.360
But you know, the quiet one
turns out to be the most volatile.

13:34.440 --> 13:35.680
This is just a stereotype.

13:36.360 --> 13:39.480
From what I was told,
Han Zi'ang is indeed an introvert.

13:39.560 --> 13:41.240
But that's because he likes to read.

13:41.320 --> 13:44.600
Of course, what he reads are comic books.

13:44.680 --> 13:48.720
Perhaps he mixed
fictional elements with reality.

13:49.520 --> 13:51.720
When he heard that Yuanlongli was haunted,

13:51.800 --> 13:53.760
he went on an adventure.

13:53.840 --> 13:55.360
He ran into a homeless guy,

13:55.960 --> 13:59.080
and then maybe, he was anxious and scared.

13:59.160 --> 14:01.960
So, he stabbed him to defend himself.

14:02.040 --> 14:08.600
Officer He, you're saying
that Han Zi'ang acted out of self-defense.

14:09.120 --> 14:10.120
I get that.

14:10.720 --> 14:13.040
But the parents don't get that.

14:13.120 --> 14:14.360
He stabbed someone.

14:14.440 --> 14:15.640
That's the truth.

14:15.720 --> 14:17.760
If he comes to school,

14:17.840 --> 14:20.640
the other parents will be worried sick.

14:23.360 --> 14:27.800
He is still unconscious in the hospital.

14:27.880 --> 14:31.200
The police are doing their best
to investigate the case.

14:31.280 --> 14:33.400
Before the truth comes out,

14:33.480 --> 14:36.320
I urge the school not to give up on him.

14:37.240 --> 14:39.600
If someone lends him a hand
at a time like this,

14:40.200 --> 14:42.200
you're not just saving his education,

14:42.960 --> 14:44.640
you're saving his life.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.440
Principal Qin.

14:48.080 --> 14:49.160
In fact,

14:50.360 --> 14:53.360
I was worse and more rebellious
than he was back then.

14:53.440 --> 14:57.960
But someone in my life
never gave up on me.

14:58.040 --> 15:03.240
He pulled me back in time
and saved my life.

15:03.320 --> 15:05.960
That's why I can be
an officer like I am now.

15:07.360 --> 15:10.120
Principal Qin, for a child,

15:11.040 --> 15:14.480
one decision can determine his whole life.

15:14.560 --> 15:18.320
I urge you to reconsider.

15:19.400 --> 15:23.400
Perhaps you can be the one
who saves Han Zi'ang.

15:27.000 --> 15:29.960
Officer He, how about this?

15:30.560 --> 15:32.960
Since Han Zi'ang is still unconscious,

15:33.040 --> 15:36.200
we'll delay his expulsion
as much as possible.

15:36.800 --> 15:38.440
Before the investigation comes to an end,

15:38.520 --> 15:40.360
I can speak on behalf of the school

15:41.160 --> 15:44.320
that if the police
provide proof that Han Zi'ang

15:44.400 --> 15:47.800
acted out of self-defense,

15:47.880 --> 15:50.360
then we can reconsider the expulsion.

15:51.880 --> 15:52.760
Okay.

15:52.840 --> 15:53.720
Thank you.

15:53.800 --> 15:55.520
Thank you, Principal Qin.

16:06.760 --> 16:10.080
Even at this age, Xiaohe is still a rebel.

16:10.160 --> 16:13.720
She just swallows whatever hardships.

16:13.800 --> 16:17.560
Sir, Xiaohe is almost like my junior.

16:17.640 --> 16:19.480
She studied for six years
to be a criminal police officer.

16:19.560 --> 16:20.640
Have faith in her.

16:21.320 --> 16:23.400
She's my daughter.
Of course, I have faith in her.

16:23.480 --> 16:25.360
I'm her dad, after all.

16:26.840 --> 16:28.760
She also grew up under your nose.

16:28.840 --> 16:30.800
But this is her first case.

16:30.880 --> 16:33.120
She needs all the support she can have.

16:35.320 --> 16:37.280
It was my first case back then too.

16:37.360 --> 16:39.360
But you didn't pamper me.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.240
Nonsense!

16:42.320 --> 16:44.320
Did you acknowledge me
as your mentor back then?

16:46.440 --> 16:49.120
The older you are,
the more grudges you hold.

16:55.600 --> 16:57.960
NOTICE, YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL
GARDEN REDEVELOPMENT MEETING

16:58.040 --> 17:00.160
THE MEETING WILL BE HELD AT 1 P.M. TODAY.

17:14.839 --> 17:16.599
Why did they seal it off?

17:17.839 --> 17:20.280
That side wasn't involved.
Why seal that place?

17:20.359 --> 17:21.560
Let's go, sir.

17:21.640 --> 17:23.800
SEALED, NANSHAN BRANCH
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU

17:25.800 --> 17:27.240
I don't think we'll find anything here.

17:28.000 --> 17:29.520
Should we go to the surveillance room?

17:30.720 --> 17:31.800
Sir.

17:32.320 --> 17:34.480
The surveillance room
was demolished a long time ago.

17:34.560 --> 17:35.480
You already know about that.

17:36.640 --> 17:37.600
Oh.

17:38.920 --> 17:40.160
Then, let's head
to the underground car park.

17:40.800 --> 17:42.120
I bet you have no idea

17:42.200 --> 17:44.920
what it has become after all these years.

17:45.000 --> 17:47.320
Sir, let's leave.

17:47.400 --> 17:48.920
Just stay out of the case.

17:49.440 --> 17:50.760
If this turns out to be a prank…

17:50.840 --> 17:53.600
Eighteen years ago,
they also said the Xu Meng case

17:53.680 --> 17:54.800
was a prank.

17:54.880 --> 17:56.240
What did you do?

18:04.080 --> 18:06.720
Sir, just tell the truth.

18:09.960 --> 18:11.880
You want to keep me here in Weiyang

18:11.960 --> 18:14.280
to investigate the case 18 years ago.

18:21.760 --> 18:23.600
Qiao lives in Yuanlongli.

18:24.120 --> 18:25.280
Don't you want to see her?

18:39.720 --> 18:40.880
Officer Ran.

18:41.840 --> 18:42.880
Qiao.

18:43.400 --> 18:45.000
Sorry to disturb you again.

18:47.840 --> 18:48.680
And this is…

18:48.760 --> 18:51.280
Hi, miss. I am He Xiaohe.

18:51.360 --> 18:53.360
My father is He Yuanhang.

18:53.440 --> 18:55.480
He works with Uncle Ran.

18:56.440 --> 18:58.560
Hi, Xiaohe. I am Qiao Suqing.

18:58.640 --> 18:59.560
It's nice to meet you.

19:02.000 --> 19:03.720
Miss, you're so pretty.

19:03.800 --> 19:07.240
No wonder Uncle Ran
brought me here specifically.

19:13.400 --> 19:15.200
Come. Come in.

19:16.400 --> 19:17.680
Change your shoes.

19:40.320 --> 19:41.200
Xiaohe.

19:41.280 --> 19:42.880
What do you want to drink?

19:42.960 --> 19:44.440
-This one.
-This one?

19:45.680 --> 19:46.880
Then, Officer Ran…

19:47.600 --> 19:48.520
Thank you.

19:49.280 --> 19:51.400
-Here.
-Thank you.

19:55.800 --> 19:58.640
Miss, your house is so clean.

19:58.720 --> 19:59.640
And it smells good too.

20:00.440 --> 20:01.760
Thank you, Xiaohe.

20:01.840 --> 20:02.920
I'm living alone.

20:03.000 --> 20:05.320
When I'm free, I like to clean my house.

20:05.400 --> 20:07.160
You're living alone?

20:07.240 --> 20:08.640
Do you have a boyfriend?

20:11.840 --> 20:12.680
No.

20:13.640 --> 20:15.120
From what I know,

20:15.200 --> 20:18.000
Uncle Ran doesn't have
a girlfriend either.

20:23.760 --> 20:25.800
Don't get me wrong.

20:25.880 --> 20:28.200
I'm just telling facts.

20:36.760 --> 20:37.880
Xiaohe.

20:37.960 --> 20:39.400
Go take a shower here.

20:39.480 --> 20:40.760
I'll come back later
to pick you up. All right?

20:40.840 --> 20:43.440
No. I have to explore the maze with you.

20:43.520 --> 20:44.600
You must stay here.

20:44.680 --> 20:46.160
Look at you now.

20:46.240 --> 20:47.880
When your father comes here,
how am I supposed to hand you back to him?

20:51.080 --> 20:52.120
Come.

20:52.200 --> 20:54.840
Xiaohe. Let's get you
all cleaned up, okay?

20:55.920 --> 20:57.360
Officer Ran, don't let me keep you.

20:57.440 --> 20:58.920
I'll take care of Xiaohe.

20:59.000 --> 21:00.080
Don't worry.

21:01.320 --> 21:02.160
Thank you.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.800
Uncle Ran, you're blushing.

21:07.040 --> 21:08.240
Am I?

21:09.320 --> 21:11.120
Let's go to the shower.

21:26.640 --> 21:27.880
Officer He.

21:28.840 --> 21:30.080
What happened to you?

21:30.160 --> 21:31.520
Is the case almost over?

21:31.600 --> 21:34.440
I'm waiting for my tip-off reward.

21:35.280 --> 21:36.360
So am I.

21:38.160 --> 21:40.240
Please supervise the young one well.

21:40.320 --> 21:43.320
Don't let him
get carried away by his needs.

21:43.840 --> 21:44.720
Young one? Who?

21:44.800 --> 21:45.960
Officer Ran.

21:46.480 --> 21:49.640
I keep seeing him visiting Unit 415.

21:49.720 --> 21:51.800
A mistress lives there.

21:52.560 --> 21:53.600
Don't make things up.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.840
I didn't.

21:54.920 --> 21:57.320
I just saw him take a little girl

21:57.400 --> 21:59.440
to the mistress's home.

22:05.520 --> 22:08.120
Du, if you are bored,

22:08.200 --> 22:11.760
study how the amazing detectives
solve the cases in your detective novels.

22:11.840 --> 22:14.280
Don't just stare at your neighbors
and spread rumors.

22:14.360 --> 22:15.640
But I…

22:17.480 --> 22:18.520
You told me

22:18.600 --> 22:20.720
to give you useful information,
didn't you?

22:21.560 --> 22:22.760
I can't believe it.

22:25.080 --> 22:26.800
Come. Eat while it's warm.

22:26.880 --> 22:27.840
Wow!

22:28.520 --> 22:29.760
Ms. Qiao.

22:29.840 --> 22:33.800
You're just like a real-life super nanny.

22:34.560 --> 22:36.160
You're a smooth-talker.

22:36.240 --> 22:37.200
Dig in.

22:43.600 --> 22:44.560
What's the matter?

22:45.520 --> 22:48.720
It'd be great if I could call you
auntie in the future.

22:49.880 --> 22:51.640
Witty, aren't you?

22:52.280 --> 22:55.200
I've never thought
of Officer Ran that way.

22:56.080 --> 22:56.920
You're lying.

22:57.600 --> 22:59.040
I'm telling the truth.

22:59.120 --> 23:01.720
I was just saying
I'd like to call you auntie.

23:01.800 --> 23:04.400
Why did you think of Uncle Ran right away?

23:06.240 --> 23:07.240
How dare you!

23:09.920 --> 23:10.920
Coming.

23:13.040 --> 23:15.800
You can't wait to see him.

23:21.320 --> 23:22.160
You're…

23:22.240 --> 23:23.120
Dad!

23:24.720 --> 23:25.880
Xiaohe.

23:26.640 --> 23:28.640
Officer He. Come in.

23:28.720 --> 23:30.600
It's okay. I'm all dusty.

23:30.680 --> 23:32.400
-I'm here to pick my kid up.
-It's okay.

23:32.480 --> 23:34.560
Dad, I went inside
a chicken coop just now.

23:34.640 --> 23:36.280
Did you go inside a pigsty or something?

23:36.360 --> 23:38.960
I didn't get into a pigsty,
but I was harassed by pigs.

23:39.840 --> 23:41.360
Officer He. Please come in.

23:41.440 --> 23:42.440
Let me get you a fresh towel.

23:43.360 --> 23:44.480
Sorry about that.

23:49.280 --> 23:51.600
You even took a shower. Where's Uncle Ran?

23:51.680 --> 23:54.600
He's solving the maze on the 18th floor.

23:54.680 --> 23:57.200
Ms. Qiao's shampoo smells so good.

23:57.280 --> 23:58.640
Her egg noodles are delicious too.

23:58.720 --> 24:02.120
Dad, you must thank her
for taking good care of me.

24:04.520 --> 24:06.200
Here, Officer He. Clean yourself.

24:06.280 --> 24:07.240
Sure. Thank you.

24:07.320 --> 24:09.000
My daughter must have troubled you a lot.

24:09.080 --> 24:11.640
Not at all. She's so obedient.

24:12.480 --> 24:13.480
Officer He, do stay here.

24:13.560 --> 24:16.520
It's okay. I'll just wipe myself quickly.

24:19.440 --> 24:21.800
Dad, I love Ms. Qiao.

24:21.880 --> 24:24.920
Can Uncle Ran bring me here often?

24:28.440 --> 24:30.960
Go. Wash the towel for Ms. Qiao.

24:49.320 --> 24:50.280
Thank you.

24:54.320 --> 24:55.240
Officer He,

24:55.840 --> 24:59.200
I know I have a bad reputation

24:59.720 --> 25:02.640
and that I should stay away
from Officer Ran.

25:05.840 --> 25:10.200
But I am not what they say I am.

25:15.120 --> 25:17.160
I only trust what I see with my own eyes.

25:17.240 --> 25:20.240
Don't take those rumors to heart.

25:20.960 --> 25:22.720
If you have done nothing wrong,

25:22.800 --> 25:26.040
there's no need
to worry about false rumors.

25:37.680 --> 25:40.520
COME TO THE OPPOSITE
OF THE FOOT MASSAGE PARLOR QUICKLY, LILI

25:44.960 --> 25:46.960
Do you have to make a call?

25:47.040 --> 25:48.360
You can use my line.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.080
It's okay.

25:50.960 --> 25:54.120
Can I trouble you
to look after Xiaohe for a while?

25:54.200 --> 25:55.680
I might have to pick her up later.

25:55.760 --> 25:56.960
Sure. No trouble at all.

25:57.040 --> 25:59.800
I couldn't be happier that Xiaohe is here.

26:00.640 --> 26:02.160
Me too.

26:03.080 --> 26:04.240
Look at her.

26:04.320 --> 26:05.360
Be a good girl.

26:06.440 --> 26:07.880
Thank you so much.

26:13.560 --> 26:17.440
FLEA MARKET

26:37.760 --> 26:40.560
THE USUAL PLACE TONIGHT AT EIGHT
SEE YOU

26:53.680 --> 26:55.120
What do you want?

26:55.200 --> 26:56.920
Look at the car plate.

26:57.440 --> 27:00.280
I am the deputy manager
at Qingsong Cement Factory.

27:00.920 --> 27:03.720
Thugs like you best not touch me.

27:07.000 --> 27:09.320
-I'm looking for you, you punk.
-For what?

27:09.400 --> 27:12.640
A guy of mine, Wolfie,

27:12.720 --> 27:14.480
was arrested by the police two days ago.

27:14.560 --> 27:16.160
Do you know what happened?

27:16.240 --> 27:17.080
No idea.

27:19.480 --> 27:20.880
Do you know or not?

27:20.960 --> 27:23.080
Yes. I know.

27:25.680 --> 27:26.520
I know.

27:28.160 --> 27:29.320
Your guy didn't kill anyone.

27:29.400 --> 27:30.640
Don't tell me everything.

27:32.320 --> 27:34.200
Just answer my question.

27:35.000 --> 27:35.840
Okay.

27:36.560 --> 27:39.120
Did Song Qingsong make the offer?

27:40.000 --> 27:41.040
No.

27:41.120 --> 27:42.080
I did.

27:42.960 --> 27:44.720
I can swear on my life. I made the offer.

27:45.320 --> 27:46.560
I'm trying to become clean, you know?

27:48.120 --> 27:49.400
Since you made the offer,

27:50.520 --> 27:51.400
pay up.

27:52.160 --> 27:53.240
Pay what?

27:53.320 --> 27:55.360
Your guy didn't even finish the job.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.800
Why should I pay up?

27:58.160 --> 27:59.600
Why? Why?

28:01.480 --> 28:02.960
Did I tell you to do that?

28:03.040 --> 28:05.040
Let's just be civil.

28:05.120 --> 28:06.280
Be professional.

28:09.000 --> 28:13.240
My guy is an important person
in the company.

28:13.760 --> 28:17.520
And because of you, he was arrested
and is still not yet released.

28:18.280 --> 28:21.000
Should we calculate the loss of profit?

28:21.080 --> 28:22.600
The loss of profit?

28:23.120 --> 28:25.240
Your guy didn't finish the job.

28:25.320 --> 28:29.000
I had to clean up after him
and deal with those two.

28:30.120 --> 28:31.640
You killed them?

28:32.840 --> 28:33.680
Right.

28:35.720 --> 28:38.280
I didn't know you were this ruthless.

28:38.360 --> 28:39.880
One slash, one life.

28:41.120 --> 28:42.280
Not bad.

28:42.360 --> 28:44.600
What about my loss of profit?

28:48.560 --> 28:49.760
That's easy.

28:51.680 --> 28:54.120
We won't extort each other.

28:55.000 --> 28:56.760
Aren't you the second in command
of the cement factory?

28:58.120 --> 28:59.200
That's an important position.

28:59.920 --> 29:03.600
Sign a contractor agreement with me
worth 300,000 yuan.

29:03.680 --> 29:04.600
You're the client.

29:04.680 --> 29:05.560
I'm the contractor.

29:06.160 --> 29:07.000
Good enough?

29:07.840 --> 29:09.880
Maybe we can just settle
the balance instead.

29:14.520 --> 29:16.480
-Will you sign it or not?
-Yes!

29:16.560 --> 29:18.040
Yes. Yes.

29:24.160 --> 29:28.120
I like how decisive you are, Mr. Wu.

29:35.080 --> 29:35.920
CONTRACTOR AGREEMENT

29:36.000 --> 29:37.320
CLIENT: WU SHANLONG
CONTRACTOR: JIN MANSHAN

29:40.360 --> 29:42.920
Tell them to tell Manlang.

29:43.440 --> 29:44.280
Okay.

29:47.600 --> 29:48.640
Speak.

29:49.560 --> 29:52.960
Ms. Zhao forbids us
from mentioning Mengmeng.

29:53.040 --> 29:55.680
My friends and I only gossip in secret.

29:56.200 --> 29:58.760
They think a client is suspicious.

30:00.320 --> 30:01.120
Who?

30:02.240 --> 30:04.640
When he came, he only asked for Mengmeng.

30:04.720 --> 30:06.480
And he paid double.

30:06.560 --> 30:08.080
We call him Mr. Sun.

30:08.160 --> 30:09.240
Mr. Sun?

30:09.880 --> 30:12.760
He was already a regular at Pattia.

30:12.840 --> 30:15.720
And he always came with a bag
of branded clothes.

30:15.800 --> 30:18.120
The brands inside were so expensive.

30:19.440 --> 30:20.880
Branded clothes.

30:22.160 --> 30:23.400
Double Fish.

30:23.920 --> 30:25.160
It's expensive.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.480
Bowls.

30:28.440 --> 30:31.360
This dress is probably
worth more than this unit.

30:35.400 --> 30:38.360
Did Mr. Sun hand out goods
from Bowls and Double Fish?

30:39.560 --> 30:42.040
Bowls and Double Fish…

30:43.800 --> 30:45.200
I can't remember.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.880
What is Mr. Sun's real name?

30:49.880 --> 30:50.800
I'm not sure.

30:53.160 --> 30:56.640
But after Mengmeng went missing,
Mr. Sun stopped showing up.

31:03.200 --> 31:07.600
Sir, I've told you what I know.

31:07.680 --> 31:10.240
I hope you can find Mengmeng soon.

31:10.320 --> 31:11.800
I'm quite worried about her.

31:13.000 --> 31:15.200
Don't worry. We've been searching for her.

31:15.280 --> 31:16.600
Your information is very important.

31:16.680 --> 31:18.360
Thank you, Lili.

31:18.440 --> 31:21.400
If there's nothing else, I have to go now.

31:23.800 --> 31:24.520
A HOME VISIT TO XU MENG’S UNCLE,
QIAO GUOQIANG.

31:24.600 --> 31:25.360
CLEAR MARKS ON THE FLOOR
BY THE FOOT OF THE BED,

31:25.440 --> 31:26.160
INDICATING IT HAS BEEN MOVED.

31:28.760 --> 31:29.720
Oh.

31:29.800 --> 31:32.480
When I was at Pattia,
a woman called Zhizhi

31:32.560 --> 31:34.400
was quite close to Mr. Sun.

31:34.480 --> 31:36.120
You can look for her.

31:42.720 --> 31:44.040
Zhizhi.

31:45.880 --> 31:47.040
Su Yuzhi.

31:49.280 --> 31:50.880
A rich guy? What's his name?

31:50.960 --> 31:52.880
Sun, I think.

31:52.960 --> 31:54.160
His name?

31:55.160 --> 31:56.360
I don't know.

32:00.360 --> 32:01.960
She lied.

32:28.960 --> 32:30.600
Adult Gaokao…

32:32.200 --> 32:34.440
I thought only students sit for exams.

32:34.520 --> 32:36.920
Adults have to do it too?

32:37.600 --> 32:39.360
It's adult gaokao.

32:39.440 --> 32:42.040
It's a chance for people like me
who never went to high school

32:42.120 --> 32:43.840
to enter a university.

32:43.920 --> 32:46.960
Oh. You want to impress Uncle Ran.

32:48.080 --> 32:50.120
You're teasing me again.

32:51.400 --> 32:54.640
Officer Ran is an ace student
from a prestigious school.

32:55.480 --> 32:59.640
I started working after junior high.

33:01.160 --> 33:03.040
So, I could only perform

33:04.360 --> 33:06.280
physical labor,
like taking care of someone.

33:06.360 --> 33:09.520
That's why I want to study hard,

33:09.600 --> 33:12.800
get a degree, and find a good job.

33:13.400 --> 33:16.200
-You can do this.
-Why do you say so?

33:16.280 --> 33:18.920
Because you are the hardworking Ms. Qiao.

33:19.000 --> 33:23.320
My mom told me that hard work
could make your dreams come true.

33:24.600 --> 33:26.000
Your mom is right.

33:30.480 --> 33:32.320
I, too, have to study hard.

33:36.400 --> 33:39.240
-Do you even understand it?
-That's why I have to study.

33:39.320 --> 33:42.520
I want to be an ace student
like Uncle Ran.

33:43.680 --> 33:45.560
Then, let's have a pinky promise.

33:45.640 --> 33:48.120
We will both
be ace students in the future.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.320
Sure.

33:50.600 --> 33:52.120
You make a pinky promise,

33:52.200 --> 33:54.200
you keep it all your life.

33:59.480 --> 34:04.480
YUZHI BOUTIQUE

34:15.639 --> 34:18.320
The latest collection.
Pick anything you like.

34:28.199 --> 34:29.239
Excuse me.

34:34.280 --> 34:36.880
Cutie. You're finally here.

34:36.960 --> 34:38.600
Are you here to treat me to hotpot?

34:39.400 --> 34:40.520
No.

34:41.199 --> 34:44.080
I'm here to ask you about Mr. Sun.

34:44.600 --> 34:46.360
You said you weren't
close to him last time.

34:46.440 --> 34:47.400
You lied.

34:49.360 --> 34:52.120
Without lying, how else
could I make you come to me?

34:54.440 --> 34:55.440
It's a game of flirting.

34:56.040 --> 34:57.200
Su Yuzhi.

34:57.280 --> 34:58.880
I brought him here.

34:58.960 --> 35:01.160
So, tell us the truth now.

35:01.240 --> 35:04.240
Cutie, what truth do you want to hear?

35:07.600 --> 35:09.960
Please tell me who Mr. Sun is.

35:11.920 --> 35:15.440
Sun's name is Sun Zhengyong.

35:15.520 --> 35:16.640
He's from Fujian.

35:16.720 --> 35:19.240
He has shares in my boutique, too.

35:19.320 --> 35:20.720
Don't get the wrong idea.

35:20.800 --> 35:22.720
We are not intimate.

35:22.800 --> 35:24.880
What about him and Xu Meng?

35:28.200 --> 35:29.400
If I tell you,

35:29.480 --> 35:31.240
will you still come to me in the future?

35:33.920 --> 35:35.680
Please… Please answer my question.

35:40.960 --> 35:43.080
Did Sun Zhengyong give this dress to you?

35:43.160 --> 35:44.640
Mind your tongue now.

35:47.960 --> 35:50.600
I bought it from him. Wholesale.

35:54.520 --> 35:55.800
FASHION BOUTIQUE

35:57.560 --> 35:59.560
This is… A counterfeit?

35:59.640 --> 36:02.040
Counterfeits sell like hot cakes.

36:02.120 --> 36:05.080
So, Sun Zhengyong
bought the authentic products,

36:05.160 --> 36:07.080
then made counterfeits
to sell them in wholesale.

36:07.680 --> 36:09.200
Cutie, you're smart.

36:09.280 --> 36:11.680
You figured it out.

36:16.480 --> 36:18.000
How does he deal
with the authentic products?

36:18.080 --> 36:21.880
Normally, he gives them to girls he likes.

36:22.600 --> 36:24.520
He gives them to Xu Meng?

36:24.600 --> 36:25.840
I guess so.

36:25.920 --> 36:27.280
He likes Mengmeng the most.

36:27.360 --> 36:30.720
Are you saying Mr. Sun has something to do
with Mengmeng's disappearance?

36:31.520 --> 36:32.440
What do you think?

36:33.640 --> 36:34.800
I don't know.

36:37.760 --> 36:39.560
I saw them argue once.

36:40.160 --> 36:41.400
When was it? And where?

36:41.480 --> 36:43.200
At Pattia.

36:43.280 --> 36:44.800
Mr. Sun was drunk.

36:44.880 --> 36:48.000
He hugged Mengmeng
and asked her to be his girlfriend.

36:48.080 --> 36:50.800
Mengmeng said no,
and Mr. Sun lost his patience.

36:50.880 --> 36:53.040
He said Mengmeng played hard to get
and looked down on him.

36:53.120 --> 36:54.480
They then argued.

36:59.640 --> 37:01.440
-And then?
-And then?

37:02.440 --> 37:04.360
You raided Pattia.

37:09.120 --> 37:12.600
Is there any place in Weiyang
that sells authentic Bowls dresses?

37:12.680 --> 37:14.880
It's a huge brand.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.760
There's one official store in Weiyang.

37:16.840 --> 37:18.280
Right inside Weiyang Mall.

37:18.360 --> 37:21.680
Can you give us the wholesale address
of Sun Zhengyong?

37:31.760 --> 37:33.000
NANMEN WHOLESALE MARKET
NANSHAN DISTRICT, WEIYANG CITY

37:33.080 --> 37:33.920
FASHION CLOTHING HALL

37:35.920 --> 37:37.120
Oh.

37:41.720 --> 37:43.360
Remember the surprise I promised you?

37:44.880 --> 37:46.560
We have a rule. We can't…

37:47.080 --> 37:48.600
I know.

37:49.480 --> 37:51.040
I'll charge you the original price.

37:51.920 --> 37:53.160
Five yuan.

37:57.240 --> 37:58.160
Take it.

37:59.120 --> 38:01.480
If you don't buy it,
she's going to lure you in again.

38:10.640 --> 38:12.440
Thank you, Su Yuzhi.

38:12.960 --> 38:14.760
I wish you a prosperous business.

38:20.720 --> 38:21.800
See you.

38:29.040 --> 38:30.120
Why not put it on now?

38:35.840 --> 38:36.680
He.

38:37.560 --> 38:39.960
I think Su Yuzhi
is telling the truth this time.

38:40.560 --> 38:41.840
Of course.

38:41.920 --> 38:43.680
She is so devoted to you.

38:43.760 --> 38:44.600
He.

38:44.680 --> 38:46.520
We're investigating a case. Be serious.

38:47.720 --> 38:48.800
Sure.

38:48.880 --> 38:51.120
Then, analyze this seriously.

38:51.720 --> 38:54.800
Perhaps Sun Zhengyong
thought Xu Meng looked down on him.

38:55.920 --> 38:58.560
His love turned into hatred,
and he killed her.

39:05.560 --> 39:06.920
YONG'S FASHION

39:07.000 --> 39:08.840
Let me meet him in his shop.

39:08.920 --> 39:12.240
I'll visit the official Bowls store
to check when he purchased the dress.

39:13.200 --> 39:14.440
Not bad.

39:14.520 --> 39:16.040
You've learned how to narrow down
the scope from me.

39:16.640 --> 39:17.840
That's progress.

39:20.800 --> 39:23.680
Also, we shouldn't give up
on the lead on Song Qingsong.

39:23.760 --> 39:25.640
Be patient. One at a time.

40:04.480 --> 40:05.320
What happened to your head?

40:05.920 --> 40:08.280
What could be so serious
that you couldn't say it on the phone?

40:09.600 --> 40:11.120
What else could it be?

40:12.120 --> 40:13.160
If it's about Song, forget it.

40:15.200 --> 40:16.360
Forget it?

40:17.160 --> 40:19.720
Wu Shanlong. Are you taking me for a fool?

40:20.320 --> 40:21.600
Two plans.

40:21.680 --> 40:23.280
And both times,
you told me they were foolproof.

40:23.360 --> 40:24.640
Then, what happened?

40:27.240 --> 40:29.560
You're putting it as if it were my fault.

40:29.640 --> 40:31.280
You came to me first,

40:31.360 --> 40:33.760
saying that we could work together
to scam money out of Song.

40:36.080 --> 40:37.400
I don't care about his money anymore.

40:38.440 --> 40:42.240
Can you even hear what you just said?

40:43.800 --> 40:45.120
The police are after Mengmeng.

40:46.320 --> 40:47.840
Song Qingsong wants me to turn myself in.

40:51.800 --> 40:55.840
So, if you turn yourself in
and they interrogate you,

40:55.920 --> 40:57.840
will you rat me out?

41:04.880 --> 41:05.720
I knew it.

41:05.800 --> 41:09.280
If men were reliable, pigs could fly.

41:11.000 --> 41:12.720
I was forced to.

41:12.800 --> 41:14.400
Do you have a plan or not?

41:14.480 --> 41:16.680
Didn't you just say my plan was useless?

41:16.760 --> 41:17.640
Zhao Hongmei,

41:17.720 --> 41:19.800
let me remind you
that we're both in the same boat.

41:24.200 --> 41:25.800
We're past the point of no return.

41:25.880 --> 41:27.880
We can't do this forever.

41:29.000 --> 41:30.200
Wu Shanlong.

41:32.400 --> 41:34.320
I want you to tell me the truth.

41:34.840 --> 41:36.200
Otherwise, forget everything.

41:36.840 --> 41:37.920
Mengmeng.

41:39.880 --> 41:42.040
Is she dead or alive?

41:44.080 --> 41:45.280
She's dead.

41:46.480 --> 41:47.800
Stone cold dead!

41:50.560 --> 41:52.360
For goodness's sake.
